  <h2 id='theme'>🎨 Theme<a class='anchor' href='#theme'>#</a></h2>
  <p>
    This theme, Astro-Axi, is heavily modified based on Astro's <a href='https://astro-pure.js.org/docs'>Pure</a>, <a
      href='https://github.com/chrismwilliams/astro-theme-cactus'>Cactus</a
    >, and <a href='https://astro-theme-resume.vercel.app/'>Resume</a> themes. Changes include decoupling components from packages into Astro-native `components`, redesigning many UI modules, rewriting pages such as Tags, adding publication interfaces, fixing bugs (e.g., BackToTop counting), and supporting i18n.
  </p>

